data.description:
It can be a challenge to find a home that is close to major roads, shopping, restaurants, and is secluded from all the noise. This house checks all those boxes. 

You'll love the large kitchen, perfect for entertaining and the large formal living/dining room. 

The master bedroom offers plenty of natural light from the bay windows and the master closet is separate from the bathroom. 

Don't let this beautiful home slip through your fingers!
